frames.caption: Three miniature construction workers are creatively posed around a frying egg in a pan. One worker is standing on a spoon, pouring salt onto the egg, while the other two observe closely. The scene humorously mimics a construction site with the egg as their project.
frames.description: The image depicts a playful and imaginative scene where tiny figures of construction workers are interacting with a frying egg as if it were a construction site. The setting is a kitchen, and the egg is being seasoned with salt by one of the figures.

frames.caption: The image depicts a whimsical scene where miniature construction workers appear to be working on a sunny-side-up egg in a frying pan. One worker is being lowered onto the egg using a spoon, while two others stand on the egg's surface, seemingly inspecting it.
frames.description: This imaginative scene combines elements of cooking and construction, creating a playful and surreal setting. The miniature figures are dressed in construction attire, adding to the illusion of a construction site on a breakfast dish.
